<p class='pleft'>The game was implemented with <a href='http://craftyjs.com' target='_blank' title='CraftyJS, a Javascript game engine'>Crafty</a>, a Javascript framework, and as well as utilising the existing Crafty components, custom components were created for walking, dialogue interactions and item management. The dialogue was stored in a JSON format. The code is open source and available on <a href='https://github.com/paxell/GameThesis/' target='_blank' title='Another World repository on Github'>GitHub</a>.</p>
